2014-03-21 Philipp Klaus Krause <pkk AT spth.de>

	* src/stm8/gen.c: Applied patch #227 by Ben Shi to fix jumping on float in y
	  and to speed up jumping on byte in yl.
	* device/lib/z80/setjmp.s:
	  Slightly more efficient longjmp().
	* device/lib/stm8/setjmp.s,
	  support/regression/tests/setjmp.c:
	  Implement setjmp() / longjmp() for stm8.
	* src/z80/ralloc2.cc: Allow use of hl in 16-bit additions with global
	  variables as long as de or bc is free.

