	* src/pic14/main.c,
	  src/pic14/main.h,
	  src/pic16/device.h,
	  src/pic16/main.c:
	  add warning if --use-non-free is *not* given while compiling
	  for PIC14 or PIC16 devices; the warning can be disabled by
	  either passing --use-non-free (usually recommended) or
	  by passing --no-warn-non-free (usually not recommended)

