	* src/pic14/gen.c (popGet): improve debugging output,
	  (SetIrp): handle PO_IMMEDIATES correctly, restructure code,
	  (genUnpackBits): handle dummy reads w/o result correctly,
	  (genNearPointerGet): handle dummy reads w/o result efficiently,
	  together this fixes #3606703
	* src/pic14/gen.c (genConstPointerGet):
	  read AOP_SIZE(result) bytes from source, fixes #3606709

