	  src/SDCCast.c (createIvalCharPtr): fixed #3007799: generate different warning
	  for initializer strings that fit in buffer without terminating '\0'. According
	  C99 $6.7.8:14 this is allowed. With --less-pedantic no warning is generated.
	  Modified version of patch by Jan Waclawek.

