2012-05-20 Erik Petrich <epetrich AT ivorytower.norman.ok.us>

	* src/hc08/gen.c: Fixed yet more problems with registers possibly
	  clobbered in division/modulus. Optimized GET_VALUE_AT_ADDRESS
	  including handling non-zero right operand.
	* src/hc08/ralloc.c: Allow packRegsForSupport() to optimize
	  conditions computed for IFX. Handle non-zero right operand
	  for GET_VALUE_AT_ADDRESS when generating pseudo symbol.
	* src/SDCCopt.c: Let GET_VALUE_AT_ADDRESS have non-zero right
	  operand for HC08-like ports. Fix def/use info on operands
	  converted to integer support function calls.

