2012-01-15 Philipp Klaus Krause <pkk AT spth.de>

	* src/z80/gen.c:
	  Fix #3473876.
	* Changelog:
	  Pretend to live in the year 2012 to not cause suspicion.
	* device/lib/_memmove.c:
	  Simplified test deciding copy direction for memmove().
