2011-11-01 Raphael Neider <rneider AT web.de>

	* src/pic14/gen.c (inc_fsr): new code to handle FSR{,0} increments,
	  (emitPtrByteGet,emitPtrByteSet): fix pointer derefence,
	  (genNearPointerGet,genNearPointerSet): fixed for enhanced cores,
	  really closes #3431024
