	* src/pic14/main.c (_pic14_do_link):
	  link with libsdcce.lib for enhanced devices

	* device/lib/Makefile.in:
	  find, copy, and rename enhanced core libraries as well

	* device/lib/pic14/NEWS:
	  document structural changes and support for enhanced cores

	* device/lib/pic14/Makefile.am,
	* device/lib/pic14/Makefile.common,
	* device/lib/pic14/Makefile.common.in (removed),
	* device/lib/pic14/Makefile.rules (removed),
	* device/lib/pic14/Makefile.subdir (removed),
