	* src/pic14/device.c, src/pic14/device.h,
	  device/include/pic14/pic14devices.txt:
	  declare enhanced cores as such
	* src/pic14/gen.c:
	  do not save/restore W, STATUS, BSR, FSRx, or PCLATH around
	  interrupts on enhanced devices, as these registers will be
	  saved automatically and FSR is not present on these devices

