	  pucure inserted into page "Visually debug for 8051 under Windows using DDD/SDCDB/S51" at
	  http://sourceforge.net/apps/trac/sdcc/wiki/Visually%20debug%20for%208051%20under%20Windows%20using%20DDD/SDCDB/S51

